('58144','20358','5','Newly built finca-style villa on a plot of 18,000 m² at 9-hole golf course'),
('58145','20359','5','This villa in Mediterranean style is situated on a private 9 hole golf course with golf hotel. At the moment the outside area and the garden of 4,000 m² is being finished. The villa is equipped with high-quality materials and first-class technology, and will be sold unfurnished. The living area of approx. 480 m² is distributed at 2 floors. On the ground floor are located the spacious living-dining area with open kitchen and laundry room, guest toilet and 2 guest bedrooms, each with bathroom en suite.\r\nOn the upper floor are two spacious bedrooms with en suite bathrooms and terraces. A large covered terrace provides shade in summertime and the 100 m² pool cool refreshment. Amenities include: under floor heating gas / water, double glazed wooden windows, stone floor tiles, air conditioning h / c and a fitted kitchen in country style. The property features also a private vineyard.\r\nThe buyer can play for free on the golf course. Furthermore, you can benefit from the hotels’ facilities such as tennis court, sauna, massage, gourmet restaurant, driving range, putting green, chipping, fitness room, 24 hour concierge service, airport limousine service, heliport, cleaning service and childcare (some of them for free).\r\nThis is the perfect home to enjoy your vacation at the highest standard. At the moment there are 3 villas for sale, have also a look at the ref. 7512 and 7513.'),
